### Test OrderItem API Endpoints

### Create a new OrderItem
POST http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tourName": "Amazing Paris Tour",
  "tourPrice": 299.99,
  "tourId": "tour123",
  "shoppingCartId": "cart456"
}

### Get all OrderItems
GET http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems

### Get OrderItem by ID (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/{{orderItemId}}

### Get OrderItems by Shopping Cart ID
GET http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/shopping-cart/cart456

### Get OrderItems count by Shopping Cart ID
GET http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/shopping-cart/cart456/count

### Get total price by Shopping Cart ID
GET http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/shopping-cart/cart456/total

### Update OrderItem (replace with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/{{orderItemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tourName": "Updated Amazing Paris Tour",
  "tourPrice": 349.99
}

### Delete OrderItem (replace with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/{{orderItemId}}

### Delete all OrderItems for Shopping Cart
DELETE http://localhost:5002/api/orderitems/shopping-cart/cart456

